---
/**
 * About Us 落地页
 */
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import PageContent from "../components/ui/PageContent.astro";

const title = "About FinCalc Hub";
const description =
  "FinCalc Hub provides free, accurate, and privacy-first financial calculators. Learn about our mission and the team behind the tools.";
---

<BaseLayout title="About Us" description={description} path="/about">
  <PageContent title={title} subtitle="Free financial tools, built with you in mind.">
    <p>
      FinCalc Hub was founded with a simple mission: to give everyone free, fast, and
      trustworthy tools to understand their money. Big financial decisions &mdash; buying a home,
      taking out a loan, planning for retirement &mdash; shouldn't require expensive software or a
      finance degree to navigate.
    </p>

    <h2>What we believe</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong>Privacy first.</strong> Your numbers belong to you. Every calculation on this
        site runs entirely in your browser &mdash; nothing you type is ever sent to our servers.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Accuracy matters.</strong> We use the same amortization and compound interest
        formulas trusted by banks and financial advisors.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Free forever.</strong> Our calculators are 100% free, no sign-up required.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Simple by design.</strong> No clutter, no confusing jargon. Just clear answers.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Our calculators</h2>
    <p>
      We currently offer five core financial calculators covering the most common money
      decisions:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/calculators/mortgage-calculator">Mortgage Calculator</a> &mdash; monthly house payments + amortization</li>
      <li><a href="/calculators/loan-calculator">Loan Calculator</a> &mdash; personal loans, debt consolidation, and more</li>
      <li><a href="/calculators/compound-interest-calculator">Compound Interest Calculator</a> &mdash; see your savings grow</li>
      <li><a href="/calculators/retirement-calculator">Retirement Calculator</a> &mdash; project your nest egg</li>
      <li><a href="/calculators/auto-loan-calculator">Auto Loan Calculator</a> &mdash; the true cost of your next car</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      More calculators are on the way. <a href="/contact">Let us know</a> what you'd like to see
      next.
    </p>

    <h2>Important disclaimer</h2>
    <p>
      We are not financial advisors, and nothing on this site should be taken as personalized
      financial advice. Our tools provide estimates to help you understand the math behind common
      financial decisions. For advice tailored to your situation, please consult a certified
      financial planner (CFP) or other qualified professional.
    </p>
  </PageContent>
</BaseLayout>
